The axioms define minimal structure.
The power comes from:

     - actions
     - morphisms
     - representations
     - classification
     - applications

SID gives the admissible structural shell.
PED supplies the operational/morphism engine.
RDG reveals the geometric, spectral, and relational content.

Group theory = symmetry encoded as:
   SID (structure)
